### ============================================================
### FOR YOU API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### ============================================================
### 1. LIST FOR YOU (default sort: paling relevan)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/for-you/jobs
### ============================================================

# @name forYouListDefault
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/for-you/jobs
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 2. LIST FOR YOU - sort baru ditambahkan
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/for-you/jobs?sort_by=baru_ditambahkan
### ============================================================

# @name forYouSortNewest
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/for-you/jobs?sort_by=baru_ditambahkan
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 3. LIST FOR YOU - sort remote/wfh
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/for-you/jobs?sort_by=remote_wfh
