### ============================================================
### 6. LIST FOR YOU - public preference context
### Endpoint:
### GET /api/public/for-you/jobs?preferred_skills[]=sql&preferred_skills[]=php&preferred_work_policies[]=remote&preferred_job_types[]=paruh_waktu&preferred_province=DKI%20Jakarta
### ============================================================

# @name forYouWithPreferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/for-you/jobs?preferred_skills[]=sql&preferred_skills[]=php&preferred_work_policies[]=remote&preferred_job_types[]=paruh_waktu&preferred_province=DKI%20Jakarta
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 7. DETAIL FOR YOU
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/for-you/jobs/{slug}
### Cara pakai:
### - Jalankan forYouListDefault
### - Copy slug dari response data[0].slug
### ============================================================

# @name forYouDetail
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/for-you/jobs/accounting-staff-1602be
Accept: application/json

###

